text: Roshumba Williams (born August 1, 1968 in Chicago, Illinois, US) is an American model. She first became known for her appearance in the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Edition in the early 1990s. She also works as an actress and reality TV show judge. Her career began in 1987. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Models from Chicago
